  "text": "After examining formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded PDAC tissue samples from 225 patients, Schultz et al. discovered five differentially expressed miRNAs, including increased level of miR-675 [CITATION_1] . Wang et al. reported that decreased miR-675-5p expression was associated with enhanced cell proliferation and patient survival in PDAC [CITATION_2] .",
